d to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Hawley was born in 1377, in Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom as the son of Robert de Hawley and Mrs. Robert de Hawley. He had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Betty Gartside. He died in 1420, in his hometown, at the age of 43."},"et":{"1377–1420":"1377–1420","1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1462":"1410–1462","1410–Male":"1410–Surnud","1370–Male":"1370–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1377":"1377","1410":"1410","1420":"1420","1430":"1430","1462":"1462","1370":"1370","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dent, Yorkshire, England":"Dent, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Dorset, Derbyshire, Eng.":"Dorset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Sutton in Craven, Yorkshire, England":"Sutton-in-Craven, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1377–1420":"1377–1420","1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1462":"1410–1462","1410–Male":"1410–Kuollut","1370–Male":"1370–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1377":"1377","1410":"1410","1420":"1420","1430":"1430","1462":"1462","1370":"1370","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dent, Yorkshire, England":"Dent, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Dorset, Derbyshire, Eng.":"Dorset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Sutton in Craven, Yorkshire, England":"Sutton-in-Craven, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1377–1420":"1377–1420","1410–1430":"1410–1430","1410–1462":"1410–1462","1410–Male":"1410–Décédé","1370–Male":"1370–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1377":"1377","1410":"1410","1420":"1420","1430":"1430","1462":"1462","1370":"1370","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Dent, Yorkshire, England":"Dent, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Dorset, Derbyshire, Eng.":"Dorset, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Sutton in Craven,